      "versionNonce": 997288290,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772802054918,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "ps -> it will show whihc task or process is running on current terminal it would give 3 4 tasks\n       not more than that\n\nps -aux -> It will show us multiple processes, Processes that are run by all the users, whihc are\n        running in the background, in foreground, in every way, It will show every process that is \n        running now in our system.\n\n        here we will see multiple things like what is pid -> process id, which command executed \n        that process, whihc user and much more",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ps -> it will show whihc task or process is running on current terminal it would give 3 4 tasks\n       not more than that\n\nps -aux -> It will show us multiple processes, Processes that are run by all the users, whihc are\n        running in the background, in foreground, in every way, It will show every process that is \n        running now in our system.\n\n        here we will see multiple things like what is pid -> process id, which command executed \n        that process, whihc user and much more",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bqHfbBTjlxMYHlpppzOqF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 938.6084676713419,
      "y": 32465.010761427915,
      "width": 1001,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
