      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772802054918,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "today we will make a cake\nHow will make a cake  -> process is we have \nfirst of all some raw ingradients\nwe will process the ingradients\nthen we will mix them processed ingradients\nand bake after that our cake is ready",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
