      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772802054918,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "lvcreate --size 300m -n lv1 vg1 -> this will create LVM of name lv1 from vg1\nlvcreate -L 300m -n lv1 vg1 -> this will also create LVM of name lv1 from vg1\nlvdisplay or lvs -> will show lvms ",
