      "originalText": "lvcreate --size 300m -n lv1 vg1 -> this will create LVM of name lv1 from vg1\nlvcreate -L 300m -n lv1 vg1 -> this will also create LVM of name lv1 from vg1\nlvdisplay or lvs -> will show lvms ",
      "autoResize": true,
