      "text": "df shows how much our disk is free\ndu shows how much disk is utilised or used\nboth of them kind of same thing\nbut we can either use df command or du command",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "df shows how much our disk is free\ndu shows how much disk is utilised or used\nboth of them kind of same thing\nbut we can either use df command or du command",
      "autoResize": true,
