      "updated": 1772804088404,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "to check DNS is responding or it is giving IP we have command\nnslookup google.com\nthe process of looking up IP from DNS or checking the IP from DNS , not connecting to the server\nit is called as DNS lookup sometimes we will say only lookup.\nLikewise one more command \ndig ip -> it is used for reverse lookup or reverse DNS lookup like it will give domaing for corresponding IP\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "to check DNS is responding or it is giving IP we have command\nnslookup google.com\nthe process of looking up IP from DNS or checking the IP from DNS , not connecting to the server\nit is called as DNS lookup sometimes we will say only lookup.\nLikewise one more command \ndig ip -> it is used for reverse lookup or reverse DNS lookup like it will give domaing for corresponding IP\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
