      "originalText": "2 ->  If TTL is zero no matter server is there or not , reachable or not, from here a packet\nwill be created like session timed our or something like and this will be sent back to client.\nthis is IP packet not tcp packet, there is many type of packets are there.\ncommand for this is \ntraceroute \nin windows it is tracert\n\nQ -> what is the meaning of each star in output of traceroute.",
