      "versionNonce": 32092478,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772819203480,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "whenever we run a process, our process is assigned a port number, All the processes are assigned a port\nnumber, basically a specific number(port) on our system on which our process is runnning.\nwebservers usually run on port 80\nhttps webservers -> 443\nssh protocol runs on -> 22\nftp runs on -> 21",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "whenever we run a process, our process is assigned a port number, All the processes are assigned a port\nnumber, basically a specific number(port) on our system on which our process is runnning.\nwebservers usually run on port 80\nhttps webservers -> 443\nssh protocol runs on -> 22\nftp runs on -> 21",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
